### Autenticação (criar usuário admin/dev)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/dev-register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin",
  "email": "admin@local",
  "password": "secret",
  "isAdmin": true
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@local",
  "password": "secret"
}

### Criar escola (admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/schools
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Escola Central"
}

### Obter dados da escola
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/schools
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar usuários da escola (membros)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar memberships (diretor)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar turma (diretor)
POST http://localhost:3000/seed-school/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "1A",
  "year": 2025
}

### Listar turmas (paginado + filtros)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/classes?page=1&limit=20&q=1A&year=2025&sort=name&order=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar disciplina (diretor)
POST http://localhost:3000/seed-school/subjects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Matemática"
}

### Listar disciplinas (paginado + busca)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/subjects?page=1&limit=20&q=mate&order=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atribuir professor a turma/disciplina (diretor)
POST http://localhost:3000/seed-school/teaching-assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teacherUserId": "{{teacherUserId}}",
  "classId": "{{classId}}",
  "subjectId": "{{subjectId}}"
}

### Listar atribuições de docência (paginado + filtros)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/teaching-assignments?page=1&limit=20&teacherUserId={{teacherUserId}}&classId={{classId}}&subjectId={{subjectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Matricular aluno em turma (diretor)
POST http://localhost:3000/seed-school/enrollments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentUserId": "{{studentUserId}}",
  "classId": "{{classId}}"
}

### Listar matrículas (paginado + filtros)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/enrollments?page=1&limit=20&classId={{classId}}&studentUserId={{studentUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar tarefa (professor)
POST http://localhost:3000/seed-school/assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classId": "{{classId}}",
  "subjectId": "{{subjectId}}",
  "title": "Trabalho 2 — Decimais",
  "dueAt": "2025-12-01T23:59:00.000Z"
}

### Listar tarefas (paginado + filtros)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/assignments?page=1&limit=20&classId={{classId}}&subjectId={{subjectId}}&q=Trabalho&sort=dueAt&order=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Enviar entrega (aluno)
POST http://localhost:3000/seed-school/submissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assignmentId": "{{assignmentId}}"
}

### Listar entregas (paginado + filtros)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/submissions?page=1&limit=20&assignmentId={{assignmentId}}&studentUserId={{studentUserId}}&order=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Lançar nota (professor)
POST http://localhost:3000/seed-school/grades
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentUserId": "{{studentUserId}}",
  "classId": "{{classId}}",
  "subjectId": "{{subjectId}}",
  "assignmentId": "{{assignmentId}}",
  "value": 9.5
}

### Listar notas (paginado + filtros)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/grades?page=1&limit=20&studentUserId={{studentUserId}}&classId={{classId}}&subjectId={{subjectId}}&order=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Registrar presença (professor)
POST http://localhost:3000/seed-school/attendance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classId": "{{classId}}",
  "studentUserId": "{{studentUserId}}",
  "date": "2025-09-01",
  "status": "PRESENT"
}

### Listar presenças (paginado + filtros)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/attendance?page=1&limit=20&classId={{classId}}&studentUserId={{studentUserId}}&dateFrom=2025-01-01&dateTo=2025-12-31&status=PRESENT&order=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar comunicado (diretor)
POST http://localhost:3000/seed-school/communications/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Reunião de Pais",
  "content": "Reunião na próxima terça, 19h.",
  "classId": "{{classId}}"
}

### Listar comunicados (paginado + busca)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/communications/announcements?page=1&limit=20&q=Reuni%C3%A3o&classId={{classId}}&order=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Enviar mensagem (qualquer membro da escola)
POST http://localhost:3000/seed-school/communications/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Olá turma!",
  "classId": "{{classId}}"
}

### Listar mensagens (paginado + filtros)
GET http://localhost:3000/seed-school/communications/messages?page=1&limit=20&q=ol%C3%A1&fromUserId={{teacherUserId}}&classId={{classId}}&order=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
